{"tid":463893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"足總副主席：播國歌喊「去廁所」無聊幼稚","createTime":"2017-11-10T03:08:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T05:41:07.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7e5fa1ad4830c4a1fcbd746872100b130072e5e3","tid":463893,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T03:08:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171110/s00001/65ff3b06d31341227c77f62ef664cdf4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171110%2Fs00001%2F65ff3b06d31341227c77f62ef664cdf4.jpg&h=c07bf1b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委會上周六通過將《國歌法》納入《基本法》附件三，港府計劃明年向立法會提交本地立法建議。香港足球代表隊昨晚友賽巴林，賽前播中國國歌時，觀眾席仍然傳出噓聲，亦有球迷大聲叫要「去廁所」離開座位。足總副主席貝鈞奇表示，昨日噓國歌的聲音較以往小，但形容大叫「去廁所」的行為是「無聊、幼稚」。<br />\n<br />\n貝鈞奇今日接受港台節目訪問時，指昨晚旺角大球場場內加強保安，又感覺到有便衣警察，貝鈞奇指，足總並無主動要求增強警力，他亦無留意到有便衣警察有沒有拍攝在場的球迷。<br />\n<br />\n貝鈞奇指，昨日賽事有監場，即使監場人員因看到球迷做出嚴重違規行為而撰寫報告，亦不會影響下周二對黎巴嫩的賽事，因就算監場報告有影響，亦需時在亞洲足協排期聆訊。"},{"pid":"0ec61de547d1b4a38ef1a1f30a6bd455704e5021","tid":463893,"uid":46332,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T03:12:12.000Z","msg":"你話黑警唔係政治工具搵邊個信<br />\n入場做乜鳩?"},{"pid":"d0e90f89c982cafe7d3c99c593923d2144c47900","tid":463893,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T03:12:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171110/s00001/1510279238037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171110%2Fs00001%2F1510279238037&d=8o8IpGvZIrFUzz0L7rZ4Fmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=fe575108\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171110%2Fs00001%2F1510279238037&h=d98a1cf4\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171110/s00001/1510279238037</a>"},{"pid":"1f106fbc4c874dbcc73c60a2d448273c7d825501","tid":463893,"uid":47259,"like":2